		<p>Kate smirked. "Okay. You win, tough stuff."</p>
		<p>This time it was Bryn's turn to raise an eyebrow. Kate was an incredibly beautiful woman. She had long, auburn hair, a peaches and cream complexion, and huge brown eyes. She wondered if there was something between the two women. They certainly seemed very familiar with each other.</p>
