		<p>Bryn awakened slowly. She glanced over at the clock/radio with bleary eyes. The dial read 10:00 a.m. She had intended on waking up earlier in case Alex needed more Tylenol, but she was just too tired, having sat up with the beautiful surgeon most of the night.</p>
