		<p>Alex sank back into the soft, down pillows as she closed her eyes. Her head still hurt a little and she was very weak. Yet, she couldn't remember when she had felt so at peace. She was certain it was due to Bryn. The way she had tenderly cared for her when she was so sick was unfathomable to the lonely surgeon.</p>
