		<p>"I'll be all right. It just went down the wrong way." She paused to catch her breath for a moment. "Listen, why don't you go home and get cleaned up. Then you can come back and go to the stables with me to ride Apollo. He's probably missing me by now."</p>
		<p>"I'd love to!" Bryn replied cheerfully. "I don't ride, but I'd love to join you."</p>
