		<p>While Bryn was gone, Alex thought back over the surprising turn of events. Bryn had come over to drop off a disc and have a short visit. Instead, she had ended up holding Alex's head while she was sick.
			<i>Last night, I even slept in her arms. Wow!</i> It had felt
			<i>so</i> good. No one had held her like that in a very long time.
		</p>
		<p>
			<i>Well, Bryn certainly didn't seem to mind</i>, Alex thought.
